  <brief_title>Effect of Intravenous Lidocaine on the Tolerability of Early Oral Feeding After Laparoscopic Colorectal Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Controlled Study for the Effect of Intravenous Lidocaine on the Tolerability of Early Oral Feeding After Laparoscopic Colorectal Surgery in Patients With Colorectal Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
